----------------------------------------------------------------
 MicroTESK Version
----------------------------------------------------------------

 2014/03/20 MicroTESK 2.0 beta
 
 MicroTESK is an open-source framework for generating test programs
 for microprocessors. It is customized for a specific microprocessor
 architecture with formal specifications in nML/Sim-nML. Test programs
 are generated on a basis of test templates that represent an abstract
 description of a test case. Flexible and convenient Ruby-based test
 template language allows creating a wide range of tests (from random
 to directed) with a minimal effort.     

